# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share this in the repository:
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used in a library, you should skip it.
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock can be gitignored in libraries.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock can be gitignored in libraries.
# pdm.lock

